entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You found something that looked important in the secret laboratory and returned it to Cale.
entries.journal_entry_description: Travel to Lok and help Cale investigate the secret laboratory.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: See what you can find in the laboratory.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Hmm....that looks interesting. I bet that is what your pal, Bib Fortuna, was looking for. Bring it back to me for an examination.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Take the Science Datapad back to Cale.
